snippet.title: Le Défilé L’Oréal Paris
snippet.description:
On Sunday, October 3rd, 2021, at 9AM (GMT-4) 3PM (GMT+2), L’Oréal Paris, official partner of Paris Fashion Week®, is back with the fourth edition of “Le Défilé L’Oréal Paris”.
 
This public outdoor runway show is open to everyone and uniting an exceptional group of spokespeople who embody self-worth. Notably, in a year which also marks the 50th anniversary of the brand’s iconic slogan, “Because we’re worth it”, the show’s theme is an ode to women’s empowerment and diversity that reflects the L’Oréal Paris’ commitment to supporting all women around the world.
 
This central value at the heart of the brand is further embodied by the training program, “Stand Up Against Street Harassment”, designed to fight against street harassment and enable women to be free to walk without fear.

Discover more about us on:
https://www.lorealparis.com/
https://www.instagram.com/lorealparis
https://www.tiktok.com/@lorealparis
https://www.facebook.com/LOrealParis/
 
Discover more about L’Oréal Paris “Stand Up Against Street Harassment” program on:
https://www.standup-international.com/
